{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/social-situations/employment-support","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Employment support ","meta_description":"The Ministry of Labor and Social Affairs offers employers and self-employed persons a number of financial contributions for maintaining and creating jobs.","content":{"processed":"<h2>Support options </h2>\n<p>The Ministry of Labor and Social Affairs offers <strong>employers and self-employed persons</strong> a number of <strong>financial support for maintaining and creating job vacancies</strong>. These contribution will help you with the recruitment of employees, their education, transport to the place of work, the creation of job opportunities for the disabled or, for example, the employment of foreigners.</p>\n<p>Before you will cancel jobs, <strong>go through all possible options</strong>. And if, on the other hand, you offer a job, <strong>don't forget to register it at the Labor Office of the Czech Republic</strong>.</p>\n<p>If you're looking for information about Antivirus programs, take a look at the <a href=\"/situace/kompenzace\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Kompenzace\">Compensation area</a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/social-situations/employment-support"},"changed":"2021-02-06T12:02:57+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2021-01-03T00:49:52+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://www.mpsv.cz/podpora-zamestnanosti-pro-zamestnavatele-a-osvc","title":"All the informations and procedures required (only in Czech) "},{"uri":"https://www.mpsv.cz/web/en","title":"The web page of Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs in English "}],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"work"},"situation_type":{"name":"Social situations","path":{"alias":"/situations/social-situations"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"people_alt"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"The pro